law.history: Repealed 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 18; repealed in part 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 7, sec. 12. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 227, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3766d-3b.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Financing acquisition and improvement of parks; revenue bonds; uniting parks in one bond issue; operating expenses; operation by management corporation.
